OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fevening sunshine to come. Remaining
OL,7,Fdry and clear overnight with the
OL,8,Fstrong winds continuing along the
OL,9,Fsouth coast. Staying warm inland
OL,10,Fleading to an uncomfortable night for
OL,11,Fsome.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FStaying largely dry and sunny
OL,14,Fon Monday, although a small chance of
OL,15,Fa few showers developing later in the
OL,16,Fday. Remaining windy near the south
OL,17,Fcoast but very warm inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
