OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FThe
OL,6,Fheatwave continuing into the middle of
OL,7,Fthe week, although there will be an
OL,8,Fincreasing risk of showers and
OL,9,Fthunderstorms, especially by Thursday.
OL,10,FWinds gradually easing.
